---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-light-blue">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">
        Tailored Solutions for Your Facility's Needs
      </h2>
      <p class="text-primary text-base md:text-lg max-w-5xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        At D2 Sanitizers, we understand that each industry has unique sanitation challenges. Our products are highly effective in killing harmful germs to ensure a clean and safe environment. In today's world, disinfectants play a crucial role in preventing the spread of infectious diseases, like colds and influenza. That's why we've developed specialized solutions to meet the strict hygiene requirements of food processing, food service and commercial kitchens. When using industrial disinfectants, it is crucial to follow essential safety precautions, including the use of personal protective equipment (PPE) and proper ventilation. Our products are trusted by professionals across multiple industries for their effectiveness, safety and ease of use. Whether you're sanitizing high-contact surfaces, ensuring footwear hygiene or maintaining equipment cleanliness, we have the products to keep your facility compliant and running smoothly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Industry Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {industries.map((industry) => (
        <a
          href={`/industries/${industry.slug}`}
          class="group bg-white rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 text-primary">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32" class="w-full h-full" set:html={industry.svg} />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Title -->
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-cyan mb-4 text-center">
            {industry.name}
          </h3>

          <!-- Description -->
          <p class="text-primary text-base leading-relaxed text-center">
            {industry.description}
          </p>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>